^ "Archived copy". Archived from the original on May 22, 2014. Retrieved 2014-05-21. 
^ "Why Is Bank of America Closing Iranian Students' Accounts? | Ryan Costello". Huffingtonpost.com. May 15, 2014. Retrieved August 23, 2014. 
^ a b Katie Rucke (May 23, 2014). "Are US Sanctions Against Iran Fostering Discriminatory Banking Practices Affecting Iranian-Americans?". Mintpressnews.com. Retrieved August 23, 2014. 
^ "Bank of america closing iranian accounts because they are from Iran". YouTube. May 16, 2014. Retrieved August 23, 2014. 
^ "ايران - BBC فارسی - نگرانی از 'بسته شدن حساب ایرانیان' در یک بانک آمریکایی". Bbc.co.uk. January 1, 1970. Retrieved August 23, 2014. 
^ Zach Carter (May 9, 2012). "CEO Defends Support for Mountaintop Removal Mining". Huffingtonpost.com. Retrieved September 29, 2015. 
^ Valerie Volcovici (May 6, 2015). "Bank of America's new policy to limit credit exposure to coal". businessinsider.com. Retrieved September 29, 2015. 


